import sys

def solve():
    (x, y) = map(int, sys.stdin.readline().split())
    if x == y:
        print(1, 1)
        return
    if y % x:
        print(0, 0)
        return
    print(1, y // x)

def main():
    t = int(input())
    while t > 0:
        t -= 1
        solve()
